    "name": "Warhammer 40,000: 星际战士2",
    "steam_appid": 2183900,
    "required_age": "18",
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/f1870f76f228ea18e47d342dd96b9113.webp?t=1772125422\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/f1870f76f228ea18e47d342dd96b9113.poster.avif?t=1772125422\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=225 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/ae4f9c47c04610ebde57cab0f6505fa5.avif?t=1772125422\" width=616 height=95 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">体验星际战士的超人技能和残暴手段。利用致命技能和毁灭性武器消灭无穷无尽的泰伦虫群。选择单人或多人模式，在恢弘的第三人称战斗中保卫帝国。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/9869fcc04bcd02aee7f382e5a30982d7.avif?t=1772125422\" width=616 height=104 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/ca8f7a4a27030ad6daf47aef22f9b075.webp?t=1772125422\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/ca8f7a4a27030ad6daf47aef22f9b075.poster.avif?t=1772125422\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=225 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在这款2011年《Space Marine》的续作中，扮演回归极限战士队列的副官德米特里安·泰图斯，对战人类的敌人，再次证明你的忠诚。在遥远星球上展开史诗级战斗，镇压银河系的恐怖乱象，并揭露黑暗秘密，击退永夜威胁。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/316d36fecc238a88a7f5530d5faf3078.avif?t=1772125422\" width=616 height=104 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/00235ebe7022261023c1166460b5937a.webp?t=1772125422\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/00235ebe7022261023c1166460b5937a.poster.avif?t=1772125422\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=225 /></picture></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">投入星系级战争中！享受激烈而血腥的快节奏第三人称动作玩法，对战屏幕上成百上千的敌人，并清除无穷无尽的泰伦虫群——Saber的专有Swarm引擎让一切成为可能。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/119969d2a3487f1a4cc5f5d4b8e0fafc.avif?t=1772125422\" width=616 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">化身为自己的星际战士，畅享残酷不止的可重玩PvE和PvP模式，不断解锁新的技能和装扮！七种独特职业可供选择，每种职业最多可解锁25项特长，将特长添加到你的每种武器上，还有海量装甲和武器装扮用来自定义外观！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/a7eb29dc14385a0cbe5ac59801ec24cc.avif?t=1772125422\" width=780 height=207 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/ee234173e7db4fe11ff8950ab36ac15b.avif?t=1772125422\" width=616 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/f5ec2b6f71789b7aae7a252f19ac439d.poster.avif?t=1772125422\" width=610 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183900/extras/f5ec2b6f71789b7aae7a252f19ac439d.mp4?t=1772125422\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在艰难的3人围攻模式下杀穿一波又一波的泰伦虫族和混沌大军，击退无穷无尽的敌袭，尽量存活更长时间。每打败一波敌人均可积累点数，用于购买弹药、装备充能、医疗激励剂等等……或者用于召唤增援，例如卡迪亚士兵、星际战士，甚至是强大的无畏机甲。</p>",
